title: I need coaching for free if possible
body: Hey i feel like i really need coaching because the old play styles that were good in the older seasons are no longer good and i feel like ive become a bad player all together. I feel like im losing my sanity so if anyone who is high elo is keen to coach me add me on league and we can talk. Ty{{champion:32}} {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}

replies.body:
Can teach you counter jungling if you want but I don't play mid very much.
